Subject: [PATCH] wined3d: Implement dual source blending.

---
 dlls/d3d11/tests/d3d11.c       |  2 +-
 dlls/wined3d/adapter_gl.c      | 10 ++++++++++
 dlls/wined3d/context.c         | 15 ++++++++++++++-
 dlls/wined3d/glsl_shader.c     | 20 +++++++++++++++++---
